     2→//! Module 7 – Model-Monitoring & Automated-Retraining Orchestrator
     3→//! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
     4→//! This module wires together the Strategy + Observer patterns to:
     5→//!   1. Collect model-serving metrics from asynchronous sources
     6→//!   2. Detect drift / SLA violations through pluggable observers
     7→//!   3. Decide—via retraining strategy—whether automated retraining should start
     8→//!   4. Emit retraining jobs into an async work-queue for downstream processing
     9→//!
    10→//! The implementation is intentionally self-contained so it can be compiled
    11→//! standalone for unit-testing, yet is ready to be integrated into the wider
    12→//! `VisuTility Orchestrator` platform.
    13→//!
    14→//! External crates used:
    15→//!   - tokio      (async runtime + channels)
    16→//!   - anyhow     (error propagation)
    17→//!   - serde      (de/serialization of metric payloads)
    18→//!   - thiserror  (typed error handling)
    19→//!   - log        (structured + leveled logging)
    20→//!   - metrics    (project-wide metrics facade)
    21→//
    22→//! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
