     4→//! Hyper-parameter Tuning, Model-Monitoring and Automated-Retraining
     5→//! ================================================================
     6→//! This module glues together three critical concerns of the VisuTility
     7→//! Orchestrator platform:
     8→//!
     9→//! 1. Strategy Pattern‐based hyper-parameter tuning
    10→//! 2. Observer Pattern‐based model monitoring
    11→//! 3. Automated retraining triggers
    12→//!
    13→//! The code is completely self-contained and can be compiled and unit-tested
    14→//! in isolation.  In the full platform the public interfaces defined here
    15→//! are re-exported by the *Model Ops* layer.
    16→//!
    17→//! Dependencies
    18→//! ------------
    19→//! The following third-party crates are required in `Cargo.toml`.
    20→//!
    21→//! ```toml
    22→//! [dependencies]
    23→//! async-trait = "0.1"
    24→//! rand        = "0.8"
    25→//! thiserror   = "1.0"
    26→//! tokio       = { version = "1", features = ["full"] }
    27→//! log         = "0.4"
    28→//! ```
    29→//!
    30→//! Note: In production, all blocking‐IO should be pushed to separate worker
    31→//! pools; here tokio is used for concise asynchronous examples.
